query:
SELECT 
  u.email,
  COUNT(DISTINCT qp.questionId) as answered,
  SUM(CASE WHEN qp.firstAttemptStatus = 'correct' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as correct
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN question_progress qp ON u.id = qp.userId
LEFT JOIN questions q ON qp.questionId = q.id
WHERE u.email LIKE '%mitarbeiter%'
  AND q.courseId = 2
GROUP BY u.id, u.email;
